<i>A massive hug between the two teammates.</i>
<i>With the captain.</i>

21:44.470 --> 21:47.223
<i>Maradona, Maradona, Maradona, goal.</i>

21:47.390 --> 21:49.976
<i>Goal, goal, goal, with his corner shot. </i>

21:50.393 --> 21:53.354
<i>Napoli climbs to the top</i>
<i>of the league table, </i>

21:53.479 --> 21:55.857
<i>thanks to the exploits</i>
<i>of its young captain,</i>

21:55.940 --> 21:57.608
<i>Diego Armando Maradona.</i>

21:57.692 --> 22:00.486
Diego, Diego, Diego, Diego, Diego!

22:21.132 --> 22:23.051
No, no, don't leave, stay.

22:33.853 --> 22:36.189
- Come on, you can't fall asleep.
- I can.

22:37.023 --> 22:38.816
- Wake up.
- No.

22:38.900 --> 22:42.695
We said it was a quickie
and then you'd go training.

22:42.820 --> 22:46.491
- No.
