22:48.659 --> 22:52.497
- Well, lunch, because it's00.
- Tell Juana to bring it.

22:53.247 --> 22:55.166
Juana isn't here, we're alone.

22:55.249 --> 22:57.335
- We're alone and I have to train?
- Yes.

22:57.418 --> 23:00.838
- Clau, stop fucking around.
- You have to go. Come on.

23:04.342 --> 23:05.843
Come on, Diego, wake up.

23:08.513 --> 23:10.056
Don't fall asleep.

23:10.598 --> 23:12.767
- That's cute, Mom.
- I love this one.

23:12.850 --> 23:14.685
That's what you'll wear?

23:14.769 --> 23:17.772
Your husband will think
you're a slut and leave you.

23:17.855 --> 23:20.942
Don't be mean, Mom.
You could wear it for Daddy.

23:21.025 --> 23:23.569
Claudia. We've been waiting for you.

23:23.653 --> 23:26.114
This is Cata Chris. She's my friend.

23:26.489 --> 23:28.491
Cristiana, very nice to meet you.

23:28.616 --> 23:29.826
Hi, how are you?

23:29.909 --> 23:32.453
Not for sleeping, for going to bed.

23:32.537 --> 23:35.790
Why don't you buy one, Claudia,
these are so nice.

23:36.415 --> 23:37.583
I don't know.

23:38.459 --> 23:39.710
How much is this one?

23:39.794 --> 23:41.212
Thirty thousand lira.

23:41.295 --> 23:42.296
No, thanks.

23:43.005 --> 23:46.092
I can give you a little discount... 27.

23:46.175 --> 23:49.470
- She'll give you a discount.
- I don't need it, don't want it.

23:50.054 --> 23:51.013
Thanks.

23:51.097 --> 23:54.267
I'll make breakfast for Diego.
I thought we were alone.

23:54.350 --> 23:55.518
I like this one.

23:55.935 --> 23:57.353
- Which one, Lili?
- This one.

23:57.436 --> 23:59.105
- Which one?
- This one.

23:59.188 --> 24:00.606
- One, Mom.
- One each.

24:00.690 --> 24:03.693
- One each.
- You can come to the house as you like...

24:04.193 --> 24:05.695
How much is that one?

24:05.778 --> 24:07.613
Should I come back?

24:07.697 --> 24:08.531
Not at all.

24:08.614 --> 24:09.907
Are you sure?

24:09.991 --> 24:11.242
- It's nothing.
- Okay.

24:13.911 --> 24:15.496
Excuse me.

24:17.707 --> 24:18.708
Hello.

24:25.464 --> 24:26.841
Did you get some sleep?

24:26.924 --> 24:28.926
- No.
- Let's see.

24:29.010 --> 24:31.596
Help me, so you're more stable.

24:39.770 --> 24:41.355
You're strong, baby.

24:41.772 --> 24:43.399
There, is that okay?

24:48.571 --> 24:50.865
- Are you hungry?
- Very.

24:51.699 --> 24:53.951
Good, I brought you something yummy.

24:55.536 --> 24:56.537
I see.

25:00.625 --> 25:01.876
Hey, baby,

25:03.169 --> 25:04.754
when I get out of here,

25:05.296 --> 25:06.881
we'll go partying.

25:07.506 --> 25:08.758
We'll play tennis.

25:09.342 --> 25:12.428
Racquet back, racquet forward. Smash.

25:12.511 --> 25:14.889
As long as you get out
of here alive, sure.

25:15.598 --> 25:19.101
The doctors don't know
if you'll make it yet.

25:19.185 --> 25:20.686
Don't be mean.

25:24.523 --> 25:26.984
Get me the remote, will you?

25:27.318 --> 25:32.198
I'm tired of watching them
fuck and screw and copulate.

25:32.281 --> 25:33.699
- I can't.
- Please.

25:33.783 --> 25:36.410
I can't. Madam's orders. You know I can't.

25:36.494 --> 25:39.747
You'll watch the news, what they say
about you and go crazy.

25:40.289 --> 25:41.791
What do the say?

25:42.250 --> 25:45.169
What stories
are these motherfuckers telling?

25:45.836 --> 25:48.381
Everything. Lots of breaking news.

25:48.464 --> 25:52.468
The latest is that they found out
you scored a goal against the English

25:52.551 --> 25:53.552
with your hand.

25:55.054 --> 25:57.098
No kidding. Really?

25:57.181 --> 25:59.267
- Yes.
- No way.

26:02.311 --> 26:03.854
- Hey.
- What?

26:03.938 --> 26:08.234
I had a ring in this finger
that I always wear.

26:08.359 --> 26:10.486
Do you know what happened?

26:10.569 --> 26:14.657
The doctors take those off to examine you.

26:15.199 --> 26:16.200
Yes.

26:16.284 --> 26:17.660
Will you check for me?

26:17.994 --> 26:19.870
- Everything good?
- Yes.

26:19.996 --> 26:21.539
- All good. Excuse me.
- Yes.

26:25.584 --> 26:28.045
- Mom.
- My baby.

26:28.671 --> 26:31.299
You won't guess who came to see you.

26:32.174 --> 26:33.592
Who?

26:33.676 --> 26:35.219
- It's a surprise.
- Hi.

26:35.678 --> 26:37.555
- How are you?
- I'll leave you.

26:37.638 --> 26:39.557
- Thanks.
- Doctor.

26:40.683 --> 26:41.892
Nice to see you.

26:41.976 --> 26:44.061
- So nice to see you.
- How are you?

26:44.145 --> 26:47.148
We're getting there. Nice hair color.

26:47.231 --> 26:48.566
Do you like it?

26:48.649 --> 26:51.277
- I'll eat your Jell-O.
- Go ahead.

26:51.360 --> 26:55.823
- Thank you. To your health.
- Thanks.

26:55.906 --> 26:57.241
How's Buenos Aires?

26:58.117 --> 26:59.035
Nice.

26:59.785 --> 27:00.828
Full of people.

27:07.585 --> 27:09.170
On the 31st, while...

27:10.963 --> 27:12.131
Everyone toasted,

27:14.050 --> 27:16.802
for a better year,

27:18.429 --> 27:20.431
I almost didn't live for two days.

27:24.060 --> 27:25.144
God...

27:26.937 --> 27:28.773
He asked me to come back.

27:28.856 --> 27:32.985
You saw the light at the end
of the tunnel and turned around,

27:33.069 --> 27:35.404
in case it was a car coming at you.

27:36.489 --> 27:38.657
Right? May I?

27:41.118 --> 27:42.620
I neglected myself.

27:44.705 --> 27:46.290
I didn't care for myself.

27:46.957 --> 27:50.002
For Dalma and Giannina's sakes,
I don't want to die.

27:50.878 --> 27:54.924
And that's great, Diego.
It's the most important thing. The kids.

27:55.007 --> 27:58.761
Your children, the family.
Terrible, God, terrible.

28:00.805 --> 28:03.682
Uruguayan soccer is terrible, Diego.

28:03.766 --> 28:06.769
They start kicking when they're young.

28:07.311 --> 28:09.772
It is terrible. Look at that.

28:14.193 --> 28:15.736
Are you okay, Diego?

28:15.820 --> 28:17.947
Look. Here, Reina cuts you off.

28:18.030 --> 28:22.326
And forces you. Pass back.
Pass to the back. No, do you understand?

28:22.410 --> 28:25.871
I want you to stand here.
I want you standing there.

28:25.955 --> 28:29.041
I don't know,
I stand where the play asks me to.

28:29.125 --> 28:31.502
No, dear.
The play doesn't ask you anything.

28:31.585 --> 28:34.630
You ask for coffee, a croissant.
The play is put together.

28:34.713 --> 28:40.344
When you are on defense, without the ball.
Look. I'll show you something.

28:41.053 --> 28:44.640
I want to show you. Look. Here, let's see?

28:44.723 --> 28:49.603
See? You're a magnet.
A natural magnet. Look. Four guys.

28:49.687 --> 28:51.647
One, two, three, four.

28:51.772 --> 28:55.109
Don't touch the screen,
you'll leave marks, Carlos.

28:55.192 --> 28:58.737
Yes, you're right.
They're all over you. They caught on.

28:58.821 --> 29:01.407
Why? They don't make a man-to-man mark.

29:01.782 --> 29:03.492
One guy and four around.

29:03.576 --> 29:06.245
Got it? What should we do?
Move without the ball.

29:06.328 --> 29:09.832
Learn to move without the ball.
You'll do that with me.

29:10.624 --> 29:12.418
Now, look.

29:12.501 --> 29:13.878
Well, I'm going to bed.

29:13.961 --> 29:16.839
Well, wait for me, I'm coming.
Don't fall asleep.

29:18.674 --> 29:20.843
- I'll wait for you.
- Bye, baby.

29:21.969 --> 29:23.095
I'll be there soon.

29:23.179 --> 29:25.347
- I'm leaving.
- Okay, Claudia, thanks.

29:25.890 --> 29:27.016
- Bye.
- Good night.

29:27.099 --> 29:28.767
Bye. Good night, Claudia.

29:28.851 --> 29:33.772
Look at that. There it is. Look.
There it is. What happened there?

29:33.856 --> 29:37.818
You ran out of legs. You were running
for nothing. That's what I want.

29:37.902 --> 29:39.904
Get the ball back. Here. Watch this.

29:39.987 --> 29:43.657
- The screen.
- Yes, the screen. Want to see the corners?

29:43.741 --> 29:46.243
- Which ones?
- I have all of them.

29:46.327 --> 29:50.372
No, I don't have them all.
Just the ones that are filmed.

29:52.500 --> 29:53.918
Go on, go on.

29:54.960 --> 29:55.878
The others.

29:57.046 --> 30:01.133
There it goes. No. Diego. Diego.
No! Diego, come back.

30:01.217 --> 30:02.718
- Where? Why?
- Come back!

30:02.801 --> 30:04.678
Don't jump, dodge them.

30:04.762 --> 30:05.971
Which way?

30:06.096 --> 30:08.724
I don't care, whichever way you want.

30:08.807 --> 30:10.643
Look this way, go that way.

30:10.726 --> 30:11.894
Let me play ball!

30:11.977 --> 30:14.438
- Look one way, go the other.
- Come on, man!

30:14.522 --> 30:17.274
You have to drive them crazy.

30:17.399 --> 30:18.651
No, don't... Come here!

30:34.708 --> 30:37.753
My mom used to say,
"If you want to play, play. But study."

30:37.836 --> 30:42.132
I went to med school in the mornings,
trained in San Lorenzo in the afternoon,

30:42.216 --> 30:43.717
and then, studied at night.

30:43.801 --> 30:45.803
- What a sacrifice, Carlos.
- Yes.

30:45.886 --> 30:49.640
I only failed pharmacology.
I'll never forget it. I studied.

30:49.723 --> 30:52.226
Just one question.
The head of department.

30:52.309 --> 30:55.354
He tells me, "I have a man in pain.

30:55.437 --> 30:58.190
Hip operation. What dosage of morphine?"

30:58.274 --> 31:01.360
I state the dosage, he says,
"Go away, you got an F."

31:01.443 --> 31:03.070
"You only asked one question."

31:03.153 --> 31:05.406
"You killed the patient.
No more questions."

31:05.489 --> 31:09.243
And, well, I had to choose
between medicine and soccer.

31:09.743 --> 31:12.204
I asked another doctor,
Chief of cardiology.

31:12.288 --> 31:14.748
I was also doing an internship
in a hospital,

31:14.832 --> 31:16.500
I said, "Doctor, what do I do?"

31:16.584 --> 31:19.295
He said, "How much do you earn?"
"I make 1100 pesos."

31:19.378 --> 31:22.506
"I make 900, carry on with the soccer".
He was right.

31:22.965 --> 31:25.759
Can I ask you a question,
since you're a doctor?

31:25.843 --> 31:28.137
There are a lot of rumors about Diego.

31:28.804 --> 31:30.055
When you see him...

31:31.140 --> 31:32.391
Do you think...

31:33.892 --> 31:36.228
Do you think Diego is using cocaine?

31:37.479 --> 31:39.773
- Don't listen to rumors, Claudia.
- I know.

31:39.857 --> 31:41.483
People do harm. Don't...

31:41.609 --> 31:44.236
I know, but if I ask him, he'll say no.

31:44.320 --> 31:50.242
No, of course, he's going to tell you no.
Look, for example. See? The bathroom.

31:50.576 --> 31:52.786
The boys in the bathroom.
They are waiting.

31:52.870 --> 31:55.539
Are they all going to pee? No.

31:55.623 --> 31:57.082
See? One comes out.

31:57.166 --> 32:01.128
And they all greet each other.
This one is as high as a kite.

32:01.587 --> 32:04.048
- Exactly.
- It's my brother-in-law, Morsa.

32:04.131 --> 32:05.883
No, not him. He may have a cold.

32:05.966 --> 32:08.927
But the ones over there, I mean those.

32:09.720 --> 32:12.848
No, not him. There he is, see?
They're having fun.

32:13.766 --> 32:15.768
Healthy fun with the family.

32:18.854 --> 32:20.522
- Dancing.
- I'll go pee.

32:20.606 --> 32:24.693
Well. Maybe he's going to pee.
They're not all going for the same.

32:25.778 --> 32:29.156
Now, this one coming out now, yes.
Look at his face.

32:31.575 --> 32:33.118
There he goes.

32:33.202 --> 32:34.578
Is he family, too?

32:34.662 --> 32:35.746
- No.
- Okay.

32:37.456 --> 32:40.167
<i>Welcome to</i>
<i>the Delle Alpi stadium in Turin,</i>

32:40.793 --> 32:46.215
<i>in this Sunday where Juventus plays</i>
<i>against Diego Maradona's Napoli,</i>

32:46.298 --> 32:48.926
<i>while Juventus is</i>
<i>lead by Michele Platini.</i>

32:51.512 --> 32:54.098
<i>The atmosphere is on fire.</i>

32:54.890 --> 32:58.519
<i>Juventus doesn't want to let Napoli win</i>

32:58.644 --> 33:02.356
<i>but we'll see,</i>
<i>Napoli is playing very well this year,</i>

33:02.439 --> 33:04.233
<i>obviously led by...</i>

33:04.692 --> 33:09.530
<i>the incredible talent of the</i>
<i>young Argentinian Diego Armando Maradona,</i>

33:10.114 --> 33:10.989
<i>its captain.</i>

33:18.872 --> 33:20.916
<i>Napoli is getting warmed up,</i>

33:20.999 --> 33:24.253
<i>we also see Diego Armando Maradona</i>
<i>on the field with his team.</i>

33:26.046 --> 33:29.550
<i>We are about to start. Tip-off.</i>

33:30.300 --> 33:32.428
<i>The game has started,</i>

33:33.011 --> 33:34.847
<i>Napoli comes forward,</i>

33:35.180 --> 33:36.724
<i>Maradona, Maradona</i>

33:37.015 --> 33:38.475
<i>Maradona comes forward</i>

33:38.559 --> 33:42.062
<i>he's kicked down on the penalty area</i>
<i>but there is no penalty.</i>

33:45.983 --> 33:47.234
<i>Here, we see him,</i>

33:47.401 --> 33:50.404
<i>incredible goal by Diego Armando Maradona</i>

33:51.405 --> 33:53.699
<i>who's able to overcome the barrier.</i>

33:53.866 --> 33:55.993
<i>The goal keeper couldn't stop it,</i>

33:56.827 --> 34:02.833
<i>Tacconi almost crashed into the left pole</i>
<i>while trying.</i>

34:03.917 --> 34:05.294
<i>Diego Armando Maradona.</i>

34:09.131 --> 34:12.384
<i>The crowd is going crazy</i>
<i>at the Delle Alpi stadium,</i>

34:12.468 --> 34:15.304
<i>in this freezing rainy day in Turin.</i>

34:15.387 --> 34:17.431
<i>Here, we see Diego Armando Maradona,</i>

34:17.556 --> 34:20.976
<i>moves away from two players,</i>
<i>he looks impossible to stop.</i>

34:21.059 --> 34:25.856
<i>He goes down, down, penalty, penalty,</i>
<i>penalty, no.</i>

34:25.939 --> 34:28.150
<i>He says no,</i>

34:28.400 --> 34:34.281
<i>and Napoli's captain gets pretty upset</i>
<i>at the referee's choice to deny him...</i>

34:40.746 --> 34:42.748
There is no sign of improvement.

34:43.332 --> 34:45.250
It seems to be getting worse.

34:46.001 --> 34:47.711
- Do you feel pain?
- Yes.

34:47.961 --> 34:49.546
- Here?
- Yes.

34:49.755 --> 34:51.298
We'll run more tests later.

34:51.381 --> 34:53.967
Meanwhile,
let's ask Professor Giannini's opinion.

34:56.637 --> 34:58.180
Doctor, are you feeling well?

34:58.764 --> 34:59.765
Yes.

35:02.434 --> 35:04.978
- Good morning.
- Good morning, doctor.

35:05.562 --> 35:08.315
So, doctor, can I still be saved?

35:15.531 --> 35:16.949
Is he deaf?

35:18.617 --> 35:21.995
Help me!

35:24.832 --> 35:27.960
What's happening? Everything okay?

35:31.463 --> 35:33.090
Is he crying?

35:33.173 --> 35:36.927
The Professor really cares
about the health of his patients.

35:37.010 --> 35:39.221
I love you very much, Diego.

35:41.098 --> 35:42.808
Do you want an autograph?

35:43.308 --> 35:44.434
Yes.

35:52.943 --> 35:58.156
To my good friend...

36:03.453 --> 36:06.540
Okay, then, professor...

36:09.042 --> 36:10.335
Can I hug you?

36:11.253 --> 36:13.130
Of course you can.

36:20.095 --> 36:21.638
Help, help.

36:22.097 --> 36:24.016
Man!

36:25.350 --> 36:27.477
I'm the one who's in bad shape here!

36:28.562 --> 36:29.980
Just my luck!

36:30.898 --> 36:33.984
"Giannini was diagnosed

36:34.359 --> 36:38.530
with an acute cardiac crisis.

36:38.989 --> 36:42.659
And after 14 hours of hospitalization,

36:43.327 --> 36:44.745
of recovery," it says,

36:45.621 --> 36:47.623
"he was discharged."

36:48.373 --> 36:50.459
The asshole was hospitalized!

36:53.712 --> 36:55.839
Shall we make a toast? To Napoli

36:55.923 --> 36:59.217
and the Neapolitans,
who are crazier than the Argentines.

37:00.844 --> 37:02.429
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

37:03.472 --> 37:04.514
Cheers.

37:10.562 --> 37:13.649
Renato, another wine bottle.

37:14.399 --> 37:16.109
Salvatore, bring them another.

37:16.902 --> 37:18.487
You're ordering another one?

37:19.863 --> 37:23.158
Renato, why is Maradona
in between those two?

37:23.283 --> 37:24.576
Who the fuck knows them?

37:24.743 --> 37:27.412
Are you kidding?
Don't you get who those people are?

37:27.496 --> 37:29.873
They are from politics, finance, sport...

37:30.207 --> 37:32.084
But they are no match to me.

37:34.294 --> 37:36.505
Sure, you want a wall all to yourself.

37:36.630 --> 37:39.925
I'll cover all the walls if you bring
a championship to Napoli.

37:40.008 --> 37:41.843
I cannot do it by myself, Renato.

37:41.927 --> 37:45.722
I need that Ferlaino
to get some help for me.

37:45.806 --> 37:51.395
We don't need Ferlaino. You are enough.
We don't need anyone else, Diego.

37:52.688 --> 37:56.483
This idiot threatens with a championship.
I'll give him a championship.

37:57.526 --> 37:59.528
Be careful, Diego.

37:59.611 --> 38:02.864
Don't bust my balls, Claudia!
Can't you see that I'm having fun?

38:02.948 --> 38:06.743
- Leave me alone!
- I told you to be careful. See how he is?

38:06.827 --> 38:09.746
He doesn't look well.
He's not well and I understand.

38:09.830 --> 38:13.875
There are a lot of changes for him.
He changed his agent, his club,

38:13.959 --> 38:15.293
but he doesn't look well.

38:15.377 --> 38:19.256
The girlfriend is always the same.
And he has the best one.

38:20.298 --> 38:22.467
- Is he doing cocaine?
- Claudia.

38:22.551 --> 38:26.221
Tell me the truth. Is that it?
Tell me, so I can help him.

38:27.305 --> 38:30.600
No. No. Claudia.

38:33.145 --> 38:36.815
I always saw you as a perfect girlfriend.

38:36.898 --> 38:40.235
You're great, you don't pressure him.

38:40.652 --> 38:43.530
You come to see him,
you stay a little while,

38:43.613 --> 38:46.783
you go back to Buenos Aires
and leave him...

38:46.867 --> 38:49.244
In love. That's the way it should be.

38:49.327 --> 38:51.872
What, you think it is
a tactic that I use?

38:51.955 --> 38:54.583
He wants to be alone,
I don't want to leave.

38:57.002 --> 39:00.088
For me... For me, you two...

39:01.256 --> 39:03.925
Listen. You are made for each other.

39:04.968 --> 39:09.806
When I see you two together, I see love.

39:11.183 --> 39:13.060
True love.

39:13.518 --> 39:16.938
You've been together
since you were very young.

39:17.022 --> 39:17.981
Yes.

39:18.106 --> 39:21.818
And, perhaps,
at this moment, when Diego is

39:23.070 --> 39:26.490
under so much pressure.
With a lot of demand,

39:27.199 --> 39:29.201
because of what's expected of him,

